
The shell scripts use the following environment variables.

	MERCURY_INT_DIR
		Directory for the Mercury library interface
		files (*.int *.int2)

	MERCURY_DEP_DIR
		Directory for the Mercury library source files,
		for use in creating the depen

	MERCURY_NC_BUILTIN
		Filename of the Mercury `nc'-compatibility file (nc_builtin.nl)

	MERCURY_LIB_DIR
		Directory for the NU-Prolog object files (*.no) of the
		Mercury library

	MERCURY_COMPILER
		Filename of the Mercury Compiler

	MERCURY_INTERPRETER
		Filename of the Mercury Interpreter

